targets.rawSql:
SELECT 
  id AS "Video ID",
  title AS "Video Title"
FROM video
WHERE "channelId" IN ($channel)
ORDER BY title

SELECT 
  SUM("viewCount") AS "Views",
  SUM(likes) AS "Likes",
  SUM(dislikes) AS "Dislikes",
  SUM("commentCount") AS "Comments"
FROM video_summary

SELECT 
  "day" AS "Best Day For Views",
  AVG("ViewCount") AS "Total Views"
FROM (
SELECT
  EXTRACT(DOW FROM "publishedAt") AS "day",
  SUM("viewCount") AS "ViewCount"
FROM video
WHERE 
  EXTRACT(YEAR FROM "publishedAt" AT TIME ZONE 'UTC') IN (2020,2021,2022,2023)
GROUP BY "day"
ORDER BY 1
) AS perDOWperYear
GROUP BY "day"
ORDER BY "Total Views" DESC
LIMIT 1

panels.title: Best Day Of The Week To Publish Videos

targets.rawSql:
SELECT 
  max_freq,
  category.title
FROM into_values((SELECT mcv_agg(1, "categoryId") FROM video)) AS values
JOIN category ON category.id = values.value
ORDER BY max_freq DESC
LIMIT 3

SELECT
  EXTRACT(DOW FROM "publishedAt") AS "Day",
  SUM("viewCount") AS "Views 2020"
FROM video
WHERE 
  EXTRACT(YEAR FROM "publishedAt" AT TIME ZONE 'UTC') = 2020
GROUP BY "Day"
ORDER BY 1

SELECT
  EXTRACT(DOW FROM "publishedAt") AS "Day",
  SUM("viewCount") AS "Views 2021"
FROM video
WHERE 
  EXTRACT(YEAR FROM "publishedAt" AT TIME ZONE 'UTC') = 2021
GROUP BY "Day"
ORDER BY 1

SELECT
  EXTRACT(DOW FROM "publishedAt") AS "Day",
  SUM("viewCount") AS "Views 2022"
FROM video
WHERE 
  EXTRACT(YEAR FROM "publishedAt" AT TIME ZONE 'UTC') = 2020
GROUP BY "Day"
ORDER BY 1

SELECT
  EXTRACT(DOW FROM "publishedAt") AS "Day",
  SUM("viewCount") AS "Views 2023"
FROM video
WHERE 
  EXTRACT(YEAR FROM "publishedAt" AT TIME ZONE 'UTC') = 2023
GROUP BY "Day"
ORDER BY 1

targets.rawSql:
SELECT 
  year AS "Year",
  SUM("videosPublished") AS "Videos Published"
FROM video_summary
GROUP BY year
ORDER BY year  DESC

WITH most AS 
  (
    SELECT
      video.id AS "Video ID",
      video.title AS "Video Title", 
      video."channelId",
      video."categoryId" AS "Category",
      MAX("viewCount") AS "Views"
    FROM
      video
    GROUP BY video.id
    ORDER BY MAX("viewCount") DESC
    LIMIT 1
  )
SELECT 
  most."Video Title",
  most."Video ID",
  channel.title AS "Channel", 
  most."channelId" AS "Channel ID",
  category.title AS "Category",
  most."Views"
FROM 
  channel, most, category
WHERE 
  channel.id = most."channelId" 
  AND category.id = most."Category"

WITH most AS 
  (
    SELECT
      video.id AS "Video ID",
      video.title AS "Video Title", 
      MAX(likes) AS "Likes",
      video."channelId",
      video."categoryId" AS "Category"
    FROM
      video
    GROUP BY video.id
    ORDER BY MAX(likes) DESC
    LIMIT 1
  )
SELECT 
  most."Video Title",
  most."Video ID", 
  channel.title AS "Channel", 
  most."channelId" AS "Channel ID",
  category.title AS "Category",
  most."Likes"
FROM 
  channel, most, category
WHERE 
  channel.id = most."channelId" 
  AND category.id = most."Category"

WITH most AS 
  (
    SELECT
      video.id AS "Video ID",
      video.title AS "Video Title", 
      MAX(dislikes) AS "Dislikes",
      video."channelId",
      video."categoryId" AS "Category"
    FROM
      video
    GROUP BY video.id
    ORDER BY MAX(dislikes) DESC
    LIMIT 1
  )
SELECT 
  most."Video Title", 
  most."Video ID",
  channel.title AS "Channel", 
  most."channelId" AS "Channel ID",
  category.title AS "Category",
  most."Dislikes"
FROM 
  channel, most, category
WHERE 
  channel.id = most."channelId" 
  AND category.id = most."Category"

WITH most AS 
  (
    SELECT
      video.id AS "Video ID",
      video.title AS "Video Title", 
      video."channelId",
      video."categoryId" AS "Category",
      MAX("commentCount") AS "Comments"
    FROM
      video
    GROUP BY video.id
    ORDER BY MAX("commentCount") DESC
    LIMIT 1
  )
SELECT 
  most."Video Title", 
  most."Video ID",
  channel.title AS "Channel", 
  most."channelId" AS "Channel ID",
  category.title AS "Category",
  most."Comments"
FROM 
  channel, most, category
WHERE 
  channel.id = most."channelId" 
  AND category.id = most."Category"

SELECT 
  SUM("videosPublished") AS "Videos Published"
FROM video_summary
WHERE year = $year 
GROUP BY "year"
ORDER BY year  DESC

SELECT
  COUNT(*) AS "Trends"
FROM trend
WHERE 
  EXTRACT(YEAR FROM "trendingDate" AT TIME ZONE 'UTC') = $year

WITH most AS 
  (
    SELECT
      "videoId",
      COUNT(*) AS "Trends"
    FROM trend
    WHERE 
      EXTRACT(YEAR FROM "trendingDate" AT TIME ZONE 'UTC') = $year
    GROUP BY "videoId"
    ORDER BY "Trends" DESC
    LIMIT 10
  )
SELECT 
  video.title AS "Video",
  most."Trends"
FROM 
  video, most
WHERE 
  video.id = most."videoId"
ORDER BY "Trends" DESC
